{"tid":618811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(全球第一巨星) The Rock: 在2016選舉時「不投票」, 現在很後悔","createTime":"2018-04-06T05:59:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T16:38:31.000Z","uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c284d6774394609c097ab9c39a1f09c47c06c59e","tid":618811,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T05:59:32.000Z","msg":"被視為現時全世界最有叫座力既嘅演員: 「The Rock」狄維莊遜（Dwayne Johnson）指他在2016選舉時選擇「不投票」, 現在很後悔.  <br />\n狄維莊遜又指特朗普（Donald Trump）證明不是人人也可以當總統.<br />\n<br />\n註: 狄維莊遜以前一直支持共和黨多年, 但在去年起改稱自己為獨立選民, 不特別支持任何一個黨.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://deadline.com/2018/04/dwayne-johnson-president-vin-diesel-rolling-stone-interview-1202358971/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdeadline.com%2F2018%2F04%2Fdwayne-johnson-president-vin-diesel-rolling-stone-interview-1202358971%2F&d=UhcK7O4HZ2YeQOuwrYoL8smB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=82cfc8a2\" target=\"_blank\">http://deadline.com/2018/04/dwayne-johnson-president-vin-diesel-rolling-stone-interview-1202358971/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nJohnson, who admits he didn&rsquo;t vote in the 2016 election and regrets it, says Trump&rsquo;s election has taught the country some lessons.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;I think in a lot of people&rsquo;s minds, what Trump has proved is that anybody can run for president,&rdquo; Johnson says. &ldquo;And in a lot of people&rsquo;s minds, what he&rsquo;s also proved is that not everybody should run for president. What I&rsquo;m sensing now is that we have to pivot back to people who have a deep-rooted knowledge of American history and politics and experience in policy and how laws get made. I think that pivot has to happen.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nStill, Johnson concedes he&rsquo;s had &ldquo;under the radar&rdquo; meetings with various politicos of all persuasions, &ldquo;Just soaking in and listening.&rdquo; But, he says, &ldquo;I feel like the best thing I can do now is, give me years.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"53c4da93d9ec0e757b318a6b585b7dd6dcd9e493","tid":618811,"uid":86330,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T06:01:47.000Z","msg":"選左個癲佬"},{"pid":"5c0ac98501f10917d07575cc5cbc136d1cafefc1","tid":618811,"uid":13718,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T06:32:50.000Z","msg":"準備洗底從政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"680ac28544148eefbabe20f853287dde754563dc","tid":618811,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T06:59:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d37713d2d86aa324064b5fb7e2e18b39939d4e5","tid":618811,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T07:00:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c79bed1643955a7c2f2c70ff874e8a4dc81a22a","tid":618811,"uid":24730,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T07:56:15.000Z","msg":"侵侵係二十年嚟最偉大總統，只有佢至治到支那，阻擋西方價值被負蝕，班柒頭唔識野"},{"pid":"b80cde298681634a1a3ac96470019defe20341c5","tid":618811,"uid":132038,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T10:42:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c71cdf68c435782383751e250437bb5fc292f829","tid":618811,"uid":5220,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T13:05:41.000Z","msg":"叫你班荷里活同行快d找數移民好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4423ffe2c5c7620d26e5fb642d80f0ae7ae8a74","tid":618811,"uid":86587,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9d37713d2d86aa324064b5fb7e2e18b39939d4e5","tid":618811,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T07:00:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T13:13:41.000Z","msg":"佢支持率高過奧巴馬喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e4c3afc5b098f531e905ad8394b1423462112a","tid":618811,"uid":65128,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T13:15:22.000Z","msg":